{
  "stem": "4187.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the psychological fact of being in a cattle truck with 70 people in that unbelievable heat, not knowing where we're being taken-- and every time the train stopped-- which was often, because they'd shunt-- they shunted somewhere, and another train would go by-- we would see these-- these gendarmes outside.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was still not Germans at this stage.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was still gendarmes outside, with the-- with the guns.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we could hear what they were saying.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they-- they were using the most awful words about the Jews in there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we knew that whatever was happening would-- wasn't happening to people, it was happening to animals.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were-- but cattle wouldn't have been shut in like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "No, cattle would-- would have had better treatment, much better treatment than we did.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was just unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I remember, as-- as one could see out every so often-- well, you could see out between these-- these wires.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I remember, somewhere, we saw a-- a building.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was-- we were going through-- must have been going through a town somewhere.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And-- and I saw-- I saw buildings not very far from the train line.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I saw someone, a woman, lean out the window with-- with-- I don't know what was in her hand.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I think it was-- I think it was a-- a small rug.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And she was obviously cleaning the rug.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And she had a-- head-- you know, one of those caps on, to keep the dust off of her hair.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the incongruity of this-- you know, I'll never forget this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was-- it was like an obscene joke.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I thought, this woman-- all of this must have gone through my head so quickly, that this woman is cleaning her flat.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
